      </th>
      <th  style="vertical-align: middle; width: 15%; border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 4px">
      Nominativo
      </th>
      <th  style="vertical-align: middle; width: 15%; border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 4px">
      Circolo di appartenenza
      </th>
      <th  style="vertical-align: middle; width: 10%; border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 4px">
      Data rinnovo
      </th>
      <th  style="vertical-align: middle; width: 10%; border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 4px">
      Scad. Cert. Med.
